-beach-bike.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>2. Meet the friendly locals<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>While driving your bike in the morning, keep an eye open for some small side paths that lead into the jungle area. Get in there and drive around with your bike and interact with the friendly locals who always have a smile for you. They will be fascinated by your appearance and will try to communicate in &#x2018;the&#x2019; best language: body language.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Find:&#xA0;<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.12go.asia\/en\/travel\/thandwe\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Bus\/Flight tickets<\/a>&#xA0;to Ngapali<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-3 is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/ngapali-most-beautiful-beach-locals.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"338\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6291 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23160039\/ngapali-most-beautiful-beach-locals.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23160039\/ngapali-most-beautiful-beach-locals-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uplo