or Inle Lake you should look to $90 for a direct flight (70 min).<br><br><strong>On a budget?<br><\/strong>The bus from Yangon to Ngapali takes 15 hours and costs around 14000 kyats ($9) per person.<br>From Bagan there is no direct bus, it takes 24 hours so you might want to budget a flight from this.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-3 is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/ngapali-most-beautiful-beach-airplane.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"338\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6303 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23160019\/ngapali-most-beautiful-beach-airplane.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23160019\/ngapali-most-beautiful-beach-airplane-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23160019\/ngapali-most-beautiful-beach-airplane-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23160019\/ngapali-most-beautiful-beach-airplane-600x600.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23160019\/ngapali-most-beautiful-beach-airplane-338x338.jpg 338w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23160019\/ngapali-most-beautiful-beach-airplane-810x810.jpg 810w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23160019\/ngapali-most-beautiful-beach-airplane-30x30.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23160019\/ngapali-most-beautiful-beach-airplane-163x163.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23160019\/ngapali-most-beautiful-beach-airplane-180x180.jpg 180w, https:\/\/static.saltinourha